item.title: Resources
item.description: Omaha RUG Meetup Sign up for the mailing list to receive news about upcoming events. Omaha Analytics Forum The Omaha Analytics Forum promotes and supports advancement of analytics, predictive analytics, and data science within the professional community of Omaha. This group is a forum to share experiences and expertise for those struggling to get value out of data. Omaha Python Users Group The Omaha Python Users Group is comprised of individuals who use the Python programming languages for fun and/or profit.

item.title: About
item.description: The mission of the Omaha R User Group is to promote the use of the R programming language and support the development of a supportive and welcoming community of R programmers by sharing our experiences and expertise with other users and those new to R. Any questions, comments, concerns you can contact us at thomas.roh@hdrinc.com.
